Tabs and Indents:
- Use tab character
  - Smart tabs
- Tab size
- Indent
- Continuation indent

Spaces:
*Objects:
- after '{'
- before '}'
- before ','
- after ','
*Includes
- after left parenthesis
- before right parenthesis
*Object fields
- before ':'
- after ':'
- before '='
- after '='
- before '+='
- after '+='
- between path and '{'
*Lists
- after '['
- before ']'
- before ','
- after ','
*References
- between '${' and path
- between '${?' and path
- before '}'

Wrapping and braces:
*Keep when reformatting
- Line breaks
- Simple objects in one line
- Simple lists in one line
- Hash comments at first column
- Double slash comments at first column
*Ensure right margin is not exceeded
*Braces/brackets placement ???
*Object entries (wrap type)
- Align when multiline
- New line after '{'
- Place '}' on new line
*List elements (wrap type)
- Align when multiline
*Object fields with ':' (wrap type)
- ':' on new line
*Object fields with '=' or '+=' (wrap type)
- '=' or '+=' on new line
*Object fields with object value (wrap type)

